WEBVTT

00:00:30.000 --> 00:00:33.000
Can I just be here?

00:00:36.000 --> 00:00:39.000
Can I speak in anger?

00:00:39.000 --> 00:00:42.000
Can I speak in shame?

00:00:44.000 --> 00:00:45.000
I'm alive and ready!

00:00:45.000 --> 00:00:46.000
Get over here!

00:00:46.000 --> 00:00:50.000
From fresh-flight memory, didn't I just have the best player there?

00:00:50.000 --> 00:00:53.000
I'm ready to start the battle of how the crew keeps all the focus while I figure out who...

00:00:53.000 --> 00:00:55.000
What does it say on my jacket?

00:00:55.000 --> 00:00:56.000
Coach!

00:00:56.000 --> 00:00:58.000
That's right, coach. Football is not a democracy.

00:00:58.000 --> 00:01:01.000
And you will do a nice thing because I know it's the best way.

00:01:02.000 --> 00:01:06.000
Now look, son. We have run this player a hundred times in practice.

00:01:06.000 --> 00:01:09.000
You don't have to see Don and know where he is. Just throw it to him.

00:01:09.000 --> 00:01:12.000
Now I want you to go out there and I want you to run the same play.

00:01:12.000 --> 00:01:15.000
And I want you to win this game for us, okay?

00:01:16.000 --> 00:01:17.000
Go ahead.

00:01:28.000 --> 00:01:33.000
Go, go, go, guys!

00:01:58.000 --> 00:02:02.000
I'm a lover of a renegade fighter.

00:02:02.000 --> 00:02:03.000
Come on, Sanchez.

00:02:03.000 --> 00:02:04.000
I'm fire.

00:02:16.000 --> 00:02:17.000
All right, listen up.

00:02:17.000 --> 00:02:20.000
There is another team eating crow tonight, gentlemen.

00:02:20.000 --> 00:02:21.000
Yeah!

00:02:21.000 --> 00:02:23.000
I don't have to tell you how important

00:02:23.000 --> 00:02:25.000
next Friday night's game is.

00:02:25.000 --> 00:02:26.000
Yeah!

00:02:26.000 --> 00:02:28.000
Not only is it going to poison the state championship,

00:02:28.000 --> 00:02:30.000
but it'll be Coach Walt's 200th win!

00:02:30.000 --> 00:02:31.000
Go, Walt!

00:02:31.000 --> 00:02:32.000
Go, Walt!

00:02:32.000 --> 00:02:33.000
Go, Walt!

00:02:33.000 --> 00:02:34.000
