00:02:56.000 --> 00:02:57.000
Go, Walt!

00:03:24.000 --> 00:03:25.000
Come on in.

00:03:26.000 --> 00:03:31.000
Principal Kwan, what brings you to this sweatbox?

00:03:31.000 --> 00:03:32.000
We've got a problem, Coach.

00:03:35.000 --> 00:03:36.000
Gee, huh?

00:03:36.000 --> 00:03:37.000
My boys?

00:03:37.000 --> 00:03:39.000
Seven of them.

00:03:39.000 --> 00:03:41.000
And they're math midterm, which means they're

00:03:41.000 --> 00:03:44.000
ineligible for next Friday's game.

00:03:44.000 --> 00:03:47.000
Well, just keep it quiet for a couple of weeks,

00:03:47.000 --> 00:03:51.000
and we'll deal with it in the off season.

00:03:51.000 --> 00:03:53.000
I'm not sweeping a major academic breach

00:03:53.000 --> 00:03:55.000
under the carpet so you can win a game.

00:03:56.000 --> 00:04:01.000
You've been here, what, six months?

00:04:01.000 --> 00:04:02.000
I've been here 25 years.

00:04:02.000 --> 00:04:04.000
We're not talking about just the game.

00:04:04.000 --> 00:04:05.000
We're talking about my legacy.

00:04:05.000 --> 00:04:07.000
I don't care about your legacy.

00:04:07.000 --> 00:04:09.000
I'm here to educate young people.

00:04:09.000 --> 00:04:11.000
I've been educating young people all my life.

00:04:11.000 --> 00:04:14.000
You know how many boys have gone on to college because of me?

00:04:14.000 --> 00:04:18.000
I've gotten good jobs on my recommendations!

00:04:18.000 --> 00:04:21.000
I know most people think you walk on water, Coach.

00:04:21.000 --> 00:04:23.000
I think you're dangerous.

00:04:23.000 --> 00:04:24.000
I've seen your temper.

00:04:24.000 --> 00:04:25.000
I've seen your methods.

00:04:25.000 --> 00:04:29.000
Just because you win doesn't make you right.

00:04:29.000 --> 00:04:31.000
On Monday, I'm suspending the players.

00:04:31.000 --> 00:04:33.000
End of story.

