00:07:36.000 --> 00:07:39.000
Look, look, I know your dad would understand.

00:07:39.000 --> 00:07:40.000
He's kind of stubborn.

00:07:40.000 --> 00:07:41.000
Yeah, I remember.

00:07:41.000 --> 00:07:44.000
Jonathan Kent was one of the best athletes I ever coached.

00:07:44.000 --> 00:07:46.000
A lot of God-given talent.

00:07:46.000 --> 00:07:49.000
It's in your genes, Kent.

00:07:49.000 --> 00:07:51.000
Actually, I'm adopted.

00:07:54.000 --> 00:07:59.000
Look, I am giving you a chance to be a part of something special, part of history.

00:07:59.000 --> 00:08:02.000
Now, I've seen you stare at your father's picture in that trophy case.

00:08:02.000 --> 00:08:05.000
Don't tell me you don't want to be a part of this.

00:08:05.000 --> 00:08:08.000
And why don't you suit up?

00:08:08.000 --> 00:08:09.000
Hey, look at Ross here.

00:08:09.000 --> 00:08:13.000
He doesn't have a lick of natural talent, but he's got a truckload of heart.

00:08:13.000 --> 00:08:14.000
Thanks, sir.

00:08:14.000 --> 00:08:15.000
I guess.

00:08:16.000 --> 00:08:18.000
Let me think about it.

00:08:18.000 --> 00:08:20.000
Fordman, get over here.

00:08:21.000 --> 00:08:22.000
Hey, Clark.

00:08:22.000 --> 00:08:24.000
