00:08:24.000 --> 00:08:27.000
How do you think Kent here would do on the field?

00:08:27.000 --> 00:08:29.000
I mean, considering our current predicament.

00:08:29.000 --> 00:08:30.000
He might do all right.

00:08:30.000 --> 00:08:31.000
Hmm.

00:08:31.000 --> 00:08:33.000
He seems afraid, though.

00:08:33.000 --> 00:08:35.000
That's not the reason, is it, Clark?

00:08:35.000 --> 00:08:36.000
It's my dad.

00:08:36.000 --> 00:08:37.000
Kent.

00:08:38.000 --> 00:08:43.000
There comes a time when you gotta step out of your father's shadow and be your own man.

00:08:43.000 --> 00:08:44.000
Now, what do you say?

00:08:44.000 --> 00:08:45.000
You ready to be your own man?

00:08:46.000 --> 00:08:47.000
How'd you find Lock?

00:08:47.000 --> 00:08:52.000
Drop dead today, Clark.

00:08:52.000 --> 00:08:53.000
Come on.

00:08:53.000 --> 00:08:54.000
What'll ya' wanna do?

00:08:54.000 --> 00:08:55.000
Just play your stupid game with me.

00:08:55.000 --> 00:08:56.000
