00:09:05.000 --> 00:09:06.000
Oh no.

00:09:06.000 --> 00:09:07.000
We'll find ya.

00:09:07.000 --> 00:09:08.000
Hey darling.

00:09:08.000 --> 00:09:09.000
I'll call you at 9 p.m.

00:09:09.000 --> 00:09:10.000
See ya on the lawyer call.

00:09:10.000 --> 00:09:11.000
Okay.

00:09:11.000 --> 00:09:12.000
Well, we'll see you.

00:09:12.000 --> 00:09:13.000
Bye, Flip.

00:09:13.000 --> 00:09:14.000
And we'll change clothes.

00:09:14.000 --> 00:09:15.000
It's all right.

00:09:15.000 --> 00:09:15.600
So we okay?

00:09:15.799 --> 00:09:16.799
This isn't about us.

00:09:17.159 --> 00:09:19.200
The guys made a mistake. I don't see what the big deal is.

00:09:19.440 --> 00:09:21.860
Whitney, they cheated. I don't know how you can support them.

00:09:22.200 --> 00:09:23.480
Because they're my friends.

00:09:23.980 --> 00:09:24.960
And they used to be yours.

00:09:25.759 --> 00:09:27.139
Do you want to tell me what's really going on here?

00:09:28.179 --> 00:09:30.240
It's just the things that I thought I knew for sure

00:09:30.240 --> 00:09:32.039
don't seem so certain anymore.

00:09:32.779 --> 00:09:33.720
I don't understand.

00:09:35.840 --> 00:09:37.500
I know how much you love football,

00:09:37.700 --> 00:09:38.899
and you're great at it,

00:09:38.980 --> 00:09:40.080
and I support you.

00:09:42.740 --> 00:09:44.600
I want to find something that I'm great at.

00:09:45.000 --> 00:09:46.120
I want to find something that I'm great at.

00:09:56.899 --> 00:09:57.559
Wait a minute.

00:09:57.759 --> 00:09:59.340
What do you mean you had to say yes?

00:09:59.600 --> 00:10:01.379
Coach Waltz sort of didn't give me a choice.

00:10:01.720 --> 00:10:02.120
Let me guess.

00:10:02.200 --> 00:10:04.559
Did he give you the be-your-own-man speech, right?

00:10:06.799 --> 00:10:08.700
Waltz's been giving that speech for 25 years.

00:10:08.779 --> 00:10:10.480
Same one. Believe me, I know.

00:10:10.860 --> 00:10:12.460
What you got to do is go there tomorrow

00:10:12.460 --> 00:10:13.519
and tell him you can't play.

00:10:13.980 --> 00:10:14.340
Dad.

00:10:14.639 --> 00:10:14.980
Dad.

00:10:14.980 --> 00:10:15.840
Please don't make me do that.

00:10:16.500 --> 00:10:18.399
Son, I'm sorry. We've already had this conversation.

00:10:18.759 --> 00:10:19.920
It's never been a conversation.

00:10:20.500 --> 00:10:22.340
I can be careful, and you don't trust me.

00:10:24.000 --> 00:10:26.460
Of course I trust you, Clark, but...

00:10:26.460 --> 00:10:27.159
But what?

00:10:28.000 --> 00:10:29.340
I'm old enough to make my own decisions.

00:10:29.360 --> 00:10:30.080
When you're out on the field,

00:10:30.180 --> 00:10:32.039
a million things can happen that can affect your judgment.

00:10:32.600 --> 00:10:34.240
I mean, if you get angry, even for just a second,

00:10:34.320 --> 00:10:37.759
or you try to impress some girl with a fancy move,

00:10:38.399 --> 00:10:39.879
somebody can get seriously hurt out there.

00:10:40.420 --> 00:10:42.960
You were meant for much more important things

00:10:42.960 --> 00:10:44.379
than winning football games.

00:10:44.980 --> 00:10:47.759
I'm sick of being punished because I have these gifts.

00:10:48.500 --> 00:10:49.759
And most parents would be happy

00:10:49.759 --> 00:10:51.440
if their son could be the star of the football team.

00:10:52.080 --> 00:10:55.980
Son, I am happy when you wake up in the morning.

00:10:57.420 --> 00:10:59.220
Now, I don't need to live vicariously

00:10:59.220 --> 00:11:00.120
through your achievements.

00:11:02.800 --> 00:11:03.659
Why would you?

00:11:04.320 --> 00:11:05.300
You got to play.

00:11:08.800 --> 00:11:10.879
I'm not signing a permission slip, Clark.

00:11:11.200 --> 00:11:12.080
You don't have to.

00:11:12.840 --> 00:11:14.759
I'm playing football, and you can't stop me.

00:11:14.980 --> 00:11:28.100
Well, if it isn't the Three Wise Men.

00:11:29.460 --> 00:11:30.360
Hello, Dominic.

00:11:30.779 --> 00:11:32.159
I'm assuming you're running late

00:11:32.159 --> 00:11:33.580
because you've been in a fencing lesson.

00:11:33.860 --> 00:11:35.460
Or have you taken up polo again?

00:11:37.379 --> 00:11:38.519
I'm not running late.

00:11:38.840 --> 00:11:40.340
I canceled this meeting, if you recall.

00:11:40.600 --> 00:11:42.960
Your father insisted that we drive down here and keep it.

00:11:43.600 --> 00:11:44.779
And when he barks,

00:11:44.779 --> 00:11:44.820
he'll say,

00:11:44.820 --> 00:11:44.960
he'll say,

00:11:44.960 --> 00:11:45.420
You jump.

00:11:47.879 --> 00:11:49.660
Have you seen the quarterly numbers?

00:11:50.100 --> 00:11:50.980
Yes, I have.

00:11:51.580 --> 00:11:53.100
We're 20% below projections.

00:11:53.440 --> 00:11:56.160
And your father wants you to take drastic action.

00:11:56.480 --> 00:11:57.120
I plan to.

00:11:58.259 --> 00:11:58.820
Good.

00:11:59.759 --> 00:12:02.200
Then I can inform him that you'll be cutting your workforce.

00:12:03.040 --> 00:12:04.259
On the contrary.

00:12:05.360 --> 00:12:07.980
You can inform him I plan on increasing my workforce.

00:12:08.620 --> 00:12:09.300
By how much?

00:12:09.660 --> 00:12:10.519
20%.

00:12:10.519 --> 00:12:15.199
Lex, I've always enjoyed your unique sense of humor.

00:12:15.699 --> 00:12:16.639
But you can't be serious.

00:12:17.620 --> 00:12:19.899
You've got to spend money to make money, Dominic.

00:12:19.899 --> 00:12:23.899
If we increase productivity and marketing while our competitors retreat,

00:12:24.480 --> 00:12:26.279
when the sector bounces back,

00:12:26.679 --> 00:12:29.159
we'll corner the market.

00:12:29.399 --> 00:12:32.179
Your father sent you to Smallville to turn the plant around.

00:12:32.299 --> 00:12:36.159
My father sent me to Smallville because he'd rather surround himself with drones

00:12:36.159 --> 00:12:39.679
than people who challenge his archaic business practices.

00:12:39.679 --> 00:12:41.399
I'll be certain to tell him that.

00:12:41.599 --> 00:12:42.039
Please do.

00:12:42.919 --> 00:12:45.319
Now, this meeting is adjourned.

00:12:49.179 --> 00:12:50.519
By the way, Dominic,

00:12:51.219 --> 00:12:53.839
tell your sister I said hi.

00:12:53.839 --> 00:12:53.899
Hi.

00:13:08.359 --> 00:13:09.500
Lana, you're home early.

00:13:09.500 --> 00:13:09.539
Did you get any news?

00:13:09.539 --> 00:13:09.579
I did.

00:13:09.579 --> 00:13:09.599
I did.

00:13:09.599 --> 00:13:09.620
I did.

00:13:09.620 --> 00:13:09.659
I did.

00:13:09.659 --> 00:13:09.679
I did.

00:13:09.679 --> 00:13:10.919
Did they cancel cheerleading practice?

00:13:11.620 --> 00:13:12.279
Sort of.

00:13:12.479 --> 00:13:12.939
